  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 425°F (220°C).",
    "Toss the zucchini, bell peppers, carrots, and red onion with olive oil, salt, and black pepper on a baking sheet.",
    "Roast in the preheated oven for 25 minutes or until the vegetables are tender.",
    "In a food processor, combine basil, pine nuts, parmesan cheese, garlic, and a pinch of salt and pepper.",
    "Process until the mixture is well combined and slightly smooth.",
    "Add the roasted vegetables to the food processor and process until well combined.",
    "Cook pasta according to package instructions.",
    "Transfer the cooked pasta to a serving dish and top with the pesto sauce.",
    "Garnish with chopped kale if desired."
